data.description: Welcome to this charming 1930s brick bungalow, a beautifully remodeled gem offering timeless character w/modern convenience.Situated in a prime location, just moments away from the interstate for effortless commuting, this home combines classic charm with contemporary comfort.The heart of this home is its beautifully updated kitchen, complete with modern appliances, ample cabinetry, making meal preparation a breeze. Whether you're hosting friends or enjoying a quiet meal, this kitchen will quickly become the hub of your home. After a long day, you'll come home to a peaceful retreat where you can unwind and recharge.The back yard is enclosed w/ a white picket fence. The generous storage building is perfect for those w/hobbies, outdoor equipment, or simply the need for additional space.Use it as a workshop, art studio, or for all your seasonal storage needs.The possibilities are endless, and your outdoor oasis is ready to be personalized to suit your lifestyle. Includes many updates.
